2812
2813bool PDFPlugin::existingSelectionContainsPoint(const WebCore::FloatPoint& locationInViewCoordinates) const
2814{
2815 PDFSelection *currentSelection = [m_pdfLayerController currentSelection];
2816 if (!currentSelection)
2817 return false;
2818
2819 IntPoint pointInPDFView = convertFromPluginToPDFView(convertFromRootViewToPlugin(roundedIntPoint(locationInViewCoordinates)));
2820 PDFSelection *selectionForWord = [m_pdfLayerController getSelectionForWordAtPoint:pointInPDFView];
2821
2822 NSUInteger currentPageIndex = [m_pdfLayerController currentPageIndex];
2823
2824 NSArray *selectionRects = [m_pdfLayerController rectsForSelectionInLayoutSpace:currentSelection];
2825 if (!selectionRects || !selectionRects.count)
2826 return false;
2827
2828 if (currentPageIndex >= selectionRects.count)
2829 currentPageIndex = selectionRects.count - 1;
2830
2831 NSArray *wordSelectionRects = [m_pdfLayerController rectsForSelectionInLayoutSpace:selectionForWord];
2832 if (!wordSelectionRects || !wordSelectionRects.count)
2833 return false;
2834
2835 NSValue *selectionBounds = [selectionRects objectAtIndex:currentPageIndex];
2836 NSValue *wordSelectionBounds = [wordSelectionRects objectAtIndex:0];
2837
2838 NSRect selectionBoundsRect = selectionBounds.rectValue;
2839 NSRect wordSelectionBoundsRect = wordSelectionBounds.rectValue;
2840 return NSIntersectsRect(wordSelectionBoundsRect, selectionBoundsRect);
2841}
2842
2843static NSPoint pointInLayoutSpaceForPointInWindowSpace(PDFLayerController* pdfLayerController, NSPoint pointInView)
2844{
2845 CGPoint point = NSPointToCGPoint(pointInView);
2846 CGPoint scrollOffset = [pdfLayerController scrollPosition];
2847 CGFloat scaleFactor = [pdfLayerController contentScaleFactor];
2848
2849 scrollOffset.y = [pdfLayerController contentSizeRespectingZoom].height - NSRectToCGRect([pdfLayerController frame]).size.height - scrollOffset.y;
2850
2851 CGPoint newPoint = CGPointMake(scrollOffset.x + point.x, scrollOffset.y + point.y);
2852 newPoint.x /= scaleFactor;
2853 newPoint.y /= scaleFactor;
2854 return NSPointFromCGPoint(newPoint);
2855}
2856
2857std::tuple<String, PDFSelection *, NSDictionary *> PDFPlugin::lookupTextAtLocation(const WebCore::FloatPoint& locationInViewCoordinates, WebHitTestResultData& data) const
2858{
2859 auto selection = [m_pdfLayerController currentSelection];
2860 if (existingSelectionContainsPoint(locationInViewCoordinates))
2861 return { selection.string, selection, nil };
2862
2863 IntPoint pointInPDFView = convertFromPluginToPDFView(convertFromRootViewToPlugin(roundedIntPoint(locationInViewCoordinates)));
2864 selection = [m_pdfLayerController getSelectionForWordAtPoint:pointInPDFView];
2865 if (!selection)
2866 return { emptyString(), nil, nil };
2867
2868 NSPoint pointInLayoutSpace = pointInLayoutSpaceForPointInWindowSpace(m_pdfLayerController.get(), pointInPDFView);
2869 PDFPage *currentPage = [[m_pdfLayerController layout] pageNearestPoint:pointInLayoutSpace currentPage:[m_pdfLayerController currentPage]];
2870 NSPoint pointInPageSpace = [[m_pdfLayerController layout] convertPoint:pointInLayoutSpace toPage:currentPage forScaleFactor:1.0];
2871
2872 for (PDFAnnotation *annotation in currentPage.annotations) {
2873 if (![annotation isKindOfClass:getPDFAnnotationLinkClass()])
2874 continue;
2875
2876 NSRect bounds = annotation.bounds;
2877 if (!NSPointInRect(pointInPageSpace, bounds))
2878 continue;
2879
2880 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_BEGIN
2881 PDFAnnotationLink *linkAnnotation = (PDFAnnotationLink *)annotation;
2882 ALLOW_DEPRECATED_DECLARATIONS_END
2883 NSURL *url = linkAnnotation.URL;
2884 if (!url)
2885 continue;
2886
2887 data.absoluteLinkURL = url.absoluteString;
2888 data.linkLabel = selection.string;
2889 return { selection.string, selection, nil };
2890 }
2891
2892 auto [lookupText, options] = DictionaryLookup::stringForPDFSelection(selection);
2893 if (!lookupText.length)
2894 return { emptyString(), selection, nil };
2895
2896 [m_pdfLayerController setCurrentSelection:selection];
2897 return { lookupText, selection, options };
2898}
2899
2900static NSRect rectInViewSpaceForRectInLayoutSpace(PDFLayerController* pdfLayerController, NSRect layoutSpaceRect)
2901{
2902 CGRect newRect = NSRectToCGRect(layoutSpaceRect);
2903 CGFloat scaleFactor = pdfLayerController.contentScaleFactor;
2904 CGPoint scrollOffset = pdfLayerController.scrollPosition;
2905
2906 scrollOffset.y = pdfLayerController.contentSizeRespectingZoom.height - NSRectToCGRect(pdfLayerController.frame).size.height - scrollOffset.y;
2907
2908 newRect.origin.x *= scaleFactor;
2909 newRect.origin.y *= scaleFactor;
2910 newRect.size.width *= scaleFactor;
2911 newRect.size.height *= scaleFactor;
2912
2913 newRect.origin.x -= scrollOffset.x;
2914 newRect.origin.y -= scrollOffset.y;
2915
2916 return NSRectFromCGRect(newRect);
2917}

2926WebCore::FloatRect PDFPlugin::rectForSelectionInRootView(PDFSelection *selection) const
2927{
2928 PDFPage *currentPage = nil;
2929 NSArray *pages = selection.pages;
2930 if (pages.count)
2931 currentPage = (PDFPage *)[pages objectAtIndex:0];
2932
2933 if (!currentPage)
2934 currentPage = [m_pdfLayerController currentPage];
2935
2936 NSRect rectInPageSpace = [selection boundsForPage:currentPage];
2937 NSRect rectInLayoutSpace = [[m_pdfLayerController layout] convertRect:rectInPageSpace fromPage:currentPage forScaleFactor:1.0];
2938 NSRect rectInView = rectInViewSpaceForRectInLayoutSpace(m_pdfLayerController.get(), rectInLayoutSpace);
2939
2940 rectInView.origin = convertFromPDFViewToRootView(IntPoint(rectInView.origin));
2941
2942 return rectInView;
2943}

2963
2964bool PDFPlugin::handleWheelEvent(const WebWheelEvent& event)
2965{
2966 PDFDisplayMode displayMode = [m_pdfLayerController displayMode];
2967
2968 if (displayMode == kPDFDisplaySinglePageContinuous || displayMode == kPDFDisplayTwoUpContinuous)
2969 return ScrollableArea::handleWheelEventForScrolling(platform(event), { });
2970
2971 NSUInteger currentPageIndex = [m_pdfLayerController currentPageIndex];
2972 bool inFirstPage = !currentPageIndex;
2973 bool inLastPage = [m_pdfLayerController lastPageIndex] == currentPageIndex;
2974
2975 bool atScrollTop = !scrollPosition().y();
2976 bool atScrollBottom = scrollPosition().y() == maximumScrollPosition().y();
2977
2978 bool inMomentumScroll = event.momentumPhase() != WebWheelEvent::PhaseNone;
2979
2980 int scrollMagnitudeThresholdForPageFlip = defaultScrollMagnitudeThresholdForPageFlip;
2981
2982 // Imprecise input devices should have a lower threshold so that "clicky" scroll wheels can flip pages.
2983 if (!event.hasPreciseScrollingDeltas())
2984 scrollMagnitudeThresholdForPageFlip = 0;
2985
2986 if (atScrollBottom && !inLastPage && event.delta().height() < 0) {
2987 if (event.delta().height() <= -scrollMagnitudeThresholdForPageFlip && !inMomentumScroll)
2988 [m_pdfLayerController gotoNextPage];
2989 return true;
2990 }
2991
2992 if (atScrollTop && !inFirstPage && event.delta().height() > 0) {
2993 if (event.delta().height() >= scrollMagnitudeThresholdForPageFlip && !inMomentumScroll) {
2994 [CATransaction begin];
2995 [m_pdfLayerController gotoPreviousPage];
2996 scrollToOffsetWithoutAnimation(maximumScrollPosition());
2997 [CATransaction commit];
2998 }
2999 return true;
3000 }
3001
3002 return ScrollableArea::handleWheelEventForScrolling(platform(event), { });
3003}

3005NSData *PDFPlugin::liveData() const
3006{
3007 if (m_activeAnnotation)
3008 m_activeAnnotation->commit();
3009
3010 // Save data straight from the resource instead of PDFKit if the document is
3011 // untouched by the user, so that PDFs which PDFKit can't display will still be downloadable.
3012 if (m_pdfDocumentWasMutated)
3013 return [m_pdfDocument dataRepresentation];
3014
3015 return rawData();
3016}
